    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super reliable, drives like a dream, and has been looked after with a lot of love. If you\u2019re looking for a dependable car that still looks great on the road and is ready for its next adventure, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions!",
