    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through its individual throttle bodies up to an 8,000 RPM redline. The ZF 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal corner-exit traction. Mechanical provenance is strong, featuring a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement\u2014essential for maintaining chassis integrity. The suspension architecture is bolstered by Bilstein dampers and refreshed bushings, ensuring the MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup remains communicative. While the exterior shows minor age-appropriate patina, the powertrain is in peak form following a recent valve adjustment and consistent 10W-60 synthetic fluid intervals.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean interior. Reliable engine. Title in hand.",
