    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and utility, presenting in well-maintained condition both inside and out. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, with only the minor road chips one would expect from careful daily use. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment featuring supple leather seating that shows minimal wear and a full suite of functional electronics, including the premium sound system and dual-zone climate control. Mechanically, the car is robust; it has been serviced at regular intervals, shifts smoothly through all gears, and sits on a set of high-quality tires with significant tread remaining. It has been a reliable companion and is ready for its next owner to drive away with confidence.",
      "price": 32500.0,
