    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive engineering, this vehicle offers a seamless integration of performance and refined styling. Meticulously maintained and showing clear pride of ownership, it represents an exceptional opportunity for the professional driver seeking a reliable, high-caliber transport solution. Each system has been thoroughly vetted to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for roadworthiness and aesthetic appeal.",
