      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! If you're looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been well-loved and is ready for its next adventure, you\u2019ve found it! This beauty runs smoothly and looks great inside and out. It\u2019s been my trusty companion for a while, and I\u2019ve taken real care to keep it in solid shape. It's perfect for daily commutes or fun weekend getaways. I'm sad to see it go, but I know it'll make its next owner very happy. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
